      "message": "The condition will be \"mwifiex \u0026\u0026 (kernel-3_18 || kerne-3_10)\" and I think the mwifiex (i.e. Marvel WiFi) part is hwdep? (while the kernel version part is definitely swdep)\n\nA similar condition is also used in network.UdevRename, maybe we can create a bug for tracking all these dependencies and removing them after elm/hana uprev?",
